name: Listened to Dear Internet Episode 86: Accidental Summons

content.html:
Dear Internet, On this weeks episode, Michael is out for Origins, if you’re going, say hi by the way! But in his place, we have special guest Christopher Badell from Greater than Games! This week we talk about what happens when your brother borrows your anime, summoning baal, and walking in the snow and playing boardgames. We would greatly appreciate if you could leave us a 5-star review on your podcast app of choice! If you want more Dear Internet, please consider supporting us on patreon through Dear Internet. Sincerely, The coHosts- Nick, Jennifer, Michael, and Tim Lanning! Apple Podcast, Spotify, RSS – follow us on Twitter!

By Dear Internet
